  "faqs": [
    {
      "question": "What is the Mono Pharmacare IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Mono Pharmacare IPO<!-- --> is a <b>SME<!-- --> <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> of <!-- -->5300000<!-- --> equity shares</b> of the face value of ₹<!-- -->10<!-- --> aggregating up to ₹<!-- -->14.84<!-- --> Crores. The issue is priced at <span>₹28 per share</span>. The minimum order quantity is <!-- -->4000<!-- -->.</p><p>The <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> <b>opens on <!-- -->August 28, 2023</b>, and <b>closes on <!-- -->August 30, 2023</b>.</p><p>Bigshare Services Pvt Ltd<!-- --> is the registrar for the <!-- -->IPO<!-- -->. The shares are proposed to be listed on <!-- -->NSE SME<!-- -->.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply in Mono Pharmacare IPO through Zerodha?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Zerodha customers can apply online in <!-- -->Mono Pharmacare IPO<!-- --> using UPI as a payment gateway. Zerodha customers can apply in <!-- -->Mono Pharmacare IPO<!-- --> by login into Zerodha Console (back office) and submitting an IPO application form.</p><p><strong>Steps to apply in <!-- -->Mono Pharmacare IPO<!-- --> through Zerodha</strong></p><ol><li>Visit the Zerodha website and login to Console.</li><li>Go to Portfolio and click the IPOs link.</li><li>Go to the '<!-- -->Mono Pharmacare IPO<!-- -->' row and click the 'Bid' button.</li><li>Enter your UPI ID, Quantity, and Price.</li><li>Submit IPO application form.</li><li>Visit the UPI App (net banking or BHIM) to approve the mandate.</li></ol><p>Visit <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Application Process Review\">Zerodha IPO Application Process Review</a> for more detail.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When Mono Pharmacare IPO will open?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The Mono Pharmacare IPO opens on August 28, 2023 and closes on August 30, 2023.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the lot size of Mono Pharmacare IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Mono Pharmacare IPO<!-- --> <b>lot size is <!-- -->4000</b>, and the <b>minimum amount required is <span>₹1,12,000</span></b>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply for Mono Pharmacare IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>You can apply in <!-- -->Mono Pharmacare IPO<!-- --> online using either <a href=\"/article/upi-payment-option-ipo-application-explained/382/\">UPI</a> or ASBA as a payment method. ASBA IPO application is available in the net banking of your bank account. UPI IPO application is offered by brokers who don't offer banking services. Read more detail about applying IPO online through <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Review\"><b>Zerodha</b></a>, <a href=\"/broker/upstox/ipo/33/\" title=\"Upstox IPO Review\">Upstox</a>, <a href=\"/broker/5paisa/ipo/4/\" title=\"5Paisa IPO Review\">5Paisa</a>, <a href=\"/broker/edelweiss_broking/ipo/34/\" title=\"Nuvama IPO Review\">Nuvama</a>, <a href=\"/broker/hdfc-securities/ipo/6/\" title=\"HDFC Bank IPO Review\">HDFC Bank</a>, and <a href=\"/broker/sbi-capital/ipo/19/\" title=\"SBI Capital IPO Review\">SBI Bank</a>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When is Mono Pharmacare IPO allotment?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The finalization of Basis of Allotment for <!-- -->Mono Pharmacare IPO<!-- --> will be done on <!-- -->Monday, September 4, 2023<!-- -->, and the allotted shares will be credited to your demat account by <!-- -->Wednesday, September 6, 2023<!-- -->. Check the <a href=\"/ipo_allotment_status/mono-pharmacare-ipo/1487/\" title=\"Mono Pharmacare IPO Allotment Status\">Mono Pharmacare IPO<!-- --> allotment status</a>.</p></div>"
    },
